1
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:09,973
[Episode 19: No More Escape]

2
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:25,079
Mom!

3
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:27,026
If you're there, say something!

4
00:01:28,528 --> 00:01:29,696
Come back!

5
00:01:29,696 --> 00:01:31,702
The tide is coming in!

6
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:34,760
Mom! Come back!

7
00:01:34,760 --> 00:01:36,439
Go back!

8
00:01:36,439 --> 00:01:38,632
You shall go back!

9
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:42,640
Mom! I can't hear you!

10
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,139
Go back!

11
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,400
Go back!

12
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,515
Come back with me!

13
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,680
Mom!

14
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:54,951
Mom!

15
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,345
Mom!

16
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,120
Mom!

17
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,513
Come home with me!

18
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:05,040
Come home with me!

19
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,440
Hurry!

20
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,760
I'm here to pick you up!

21
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:09,922
I don't want to go back.

22
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:13,077
I'm here to pick you up!

23
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:16,520
When you were called to the school,

24
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,240
I also felt embarrassed,

25
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,520
regretful,

26
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:20,919
and wanted to escape.

27
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:22,759
But you were well-dressed,

28
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:24,480
holding my hand,

29
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:27,201
protecting me in your way.

30
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:31,872
So let me pick you up, okay?

31
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,656
Come back with me, okay?

32
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:39,280
No more faked wealth,

33
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,412
faked foreign life,

34
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:44,723
knock-offs,

35
00:02:45,533 --> 00:02:48,160
and lies.

36
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:50,887
I don't want to be a liar anymore.

37
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:53,647
I don't want to lie anymore.

38
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:56,480
Come back with me, okay?

39
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:58,040
Mom!

40
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,640
Please come back!

41
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:03,000
Let's stop escaping, okay?

42
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,626
Then I'll die with you!

43
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:09,725
But I don't want to die, Mom!

44
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,680
Mom!

45
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:13,240
Xi Zhou!

46
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,999
Come home with me!

47
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:16,680
- Xi Zhou!
- Mom!

48
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,216
Ren Xi Zhou!

49
00:03:18,216 --> 00:03:19,240
I got you!

50
00:03:19,240 --> 00:03:21,143
- I got you!
- Get up!

51
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,879
Slowly. Hold on.

52
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:27,206
Get up.

53
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,374
Be careful. Get up.

54
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,093
Mom.

55
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:34,332
Come on, push.

56
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,560
I'll take you home.

57
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,951
- Be careful.
- Hold me.

58
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,331
- Hold on tight.
- Be careful.

59
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:58,520
[Closed]

60
00:03:58,520 --> 00:04:00,680
I really value this opportunity.

61
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,479
A typhoon caused an outage,

62
00:04:02,479 --> 00:04:03,640
and I couldn't log in.

63
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:05,760
Could you please make an exception?

64
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:12,440
<i>If the kettle has no boiling water,</i>

65
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,680
<i>will you get angry?</i>

66
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,176
<i>Yes,</i>

67
00:04:15,176 --> 00:04:17,180
<i>because it's insincere.</i>

68
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,800
<i>You're not that kind of person,</i>

69
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,095
<i>are you?</i>

70
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:25,240
<i>Sure.</i>

71
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,439
<i>I always say "Excuse me".</i>

72
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:29,840
<i>No more faked wealth,</i>

73
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:31,946
<i>faked foreign life,</i>

74
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:35,196
<i>knock-offs,</i>

75
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,720
<i>I don't want to be a liar anymore.</i>

76
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:40,679
<i>I don't want to lie anymore.</i>

77
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,800
<i>So,</i>

78
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,560
<i>you've been lying to me all along.</i>

79
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,898
Unused. Brand new.

80
00:04:50,473 --> 00:04:51,597
Sorry.

81
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:53,439
It's okay.

82
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:55,680
Just that I might catch a cold.

83
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,080
No big deal.

84
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:59,033
Everyone can be muddled.

85
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,215
Sorry.

86
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:19,439
It's so sticky!

87
00:05:19,439 --> 00:05:22,120
Ren Xi Zhou, can I take a shower in your home?

88
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:23,840
I'll get you changed.

89
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,032
Let's go.

90
00:05:42,265 --> 00:05:44,040
Jiang He said

91
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,615
you were interviewed for their cast.

92
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:05,879
It's still raining.

93
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:08,000
I asked them to stay for some hot soup

94
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:09,841
and wait till the rain stops.

95
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,161
Oh.

96
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,112
I apologized.

97
00:06:15,112 --> 00:06:16,789
Nothing was said about you.

98
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:20,647
Oh.

99
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:23,520
What's with all the "ohs"?

100
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,813
Say something.

101
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:32,579
I just wanted to sit quietly for a while.

102
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:36,099
You came unexpectedly. I felt so ashamed.

103
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:37,976
I thought,

104
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:40,584
I might as well not go back.

105
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:42,770
Because of me?

106
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:47,386
I thought about

107
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,826
walking into the sea.

108
00:06:50,639 --> 00:06:52,280
I was a little scared,

109
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:54,118
and didn't know what to do.

110
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,521
Mom is sorry.

111
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,825
So we're even.

112
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:07,920
You used to take me home.

113
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,751
Now I take you home.

114
00:07:10,840 --> 00:07:13,200
Let's live well from now on.

115
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,842
Neither of us is sorry.

116
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:23,560
But we did trouble them.

117
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:25,880
Apologize to them later,

118
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,097
okay?

119
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,241
Okay.

120
00:07:30,241 --> 00:07:31,955
I'll follow your lead.

121
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,400
- Thank you, Auntie Ren.
- I'll bring drinks.

122
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,704
Thank you.

123
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,560
I... Let me see what else I can make.

124
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,665
The noodles are just so-so.

125
00:08:09,665 --> 00:08:10,813
Bullshit!

126
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,584
It's you, Hong Xia.

127
00:08:12,584 --> 00:08:14,625
I thought it was someone else.

128
00:08:24,052 --> 00:08:25,584
I'm sorry, everyone.

129
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,840
It's okay.

130
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:32,000
You're so polite. I'm not used to it.

131
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,284
Sit, sit, sit.

132
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:37,536
It's no big deal, okay?

133
00:08:37,536 --> 00:08:38,559
Auntie Qiu,

134
00:08:38,559 --> 00:08:41,350
welcome to try our new dishes next time.

135
00:08:41,350 --> 00:08:42,572
Okay.

136
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:51,152
I didn't mean it.

137
00:08:51,152 --> 00:08:52,590
I was a jerk.

138
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,039
It's okay.

139
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:58,880
I cursed you too.

140
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,780
You cursed me?

141
00:09:12,859 --> 00:09:14,052
I'm sorry.

142
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:16,440
Nan Xi told me

143
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,408
you missed the audition.

144
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:23,216
I'm handsome. I have plenty of chances,

145
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:24,986
right?

146
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:47,344
I'm sorry.

147
00:09:57,665 --> 00:09:58,728
Auntie,

148
00:09:58,728 --> 00:10:00,600
I want more noodles.

149
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,160
I'm so hungry.

150
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:03,320
I'll bring some for you.

151
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,772
Thank you, Auntie.

152
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,725
Mom, I'll do it.

153
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:11,120
Thank you, Xi Zhou.

154
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,201
- Have a seat. Here.
- Please sit, Auntie.

155
00:10:29,491 --> 00:10:31,279
It's better if we keep our distance.

156
00:10:31,279 --> 00:10:32,655
Again?

157
00:10:36,520 --> 00:10:37,637
Hey.

158
00:10:39,713 --> 00:10:40,840
How much?

159
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:42,024
20 yuan.

160
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,799
Will it rain?

161
00:10:52,799 --> 00:10:54,835
The typhoon is forecast to turn.

162
00:10:57,456 --> 00:10:59,194
Hey, where are you going?

163
00:11:04,560 --> 00:11:05,840
Stay away from me.

164
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,710
I hate liars.

165
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,682
Your umbrella.

166
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,879
I'm returning the favor.

167
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:14,900
What?

168
00:11:15,507 --> 00:11:17,120
You lent me an umbrella.

169
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:19,240
I lost it last night.

170
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:21,360
So I bought a new one to return to you.

171
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:23,027
We're even now.

172
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,638
Are you playing dumb?

173
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:34,582
I... don't remember.

174
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:42,640
You said you don't remember,

175
00:11:42,640 --> 00:11:45,850
I even doubt if it's true.

176
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:49,000
It's true.

177
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,760
How can I believe that?

178
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:53,640
After all, you tell a lie like it's true,

179
00:11:53,640 --> 00:11:55,093
don't you?

180
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,200
After high school,

181
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:02,039
we were in a long-distance

182
00:12:02,039 --> 00:12:03,920
relationship for four years,

183
00:12:03,920 --> 00:12:06,120
but you refused to meet me even once,

184
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:09,160
and I had to beg for your reply on WeChat.

185
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,480
You said you were busy

186
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,039
and studying abroad.

187
00:12:12,039 --> 00:12:13,720
There's the time difference. Okay.

188
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:14,960
I sent you letters.

189
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,720
I waited for you to come back.

190
00:12:16,720 --> 00:12:18,055
And then?

191
00:12:20,103 --> 00:12:21,240
And then you said

192
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:23,399
you found a better job abroad.

193
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,759
You were used to a comfortable life.

194
00:12:24,759 --> 00:12:26,240
You said I was poor, too poor

195
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:28,135
to afford the life you wanted!

196
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:33,012
My grandma was sick then.

197
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,960
I wrote scripts by her bedside during the day,

198
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,800
and found time
to write letters to you at night,

199
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:39,440
to beg you

200
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,175
to wait for me.

201
00:12:46,280 --> 00:12:47,613
I'm sorry.

202
00:12:50,520 --> 00:12:52,200
I accepted any scripts,

203
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,159
even if low-paid,

204
00:12:54,159 --> 00:12:55,520
not credited,

205
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:58,280
repeatedly revised,

206
00:12:58,280 --> 00:13:01,160
I did, until now.

207
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:03,679
You asked me why
I didn't talk about art or ideals.

208
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:05,480
But you dared not hear my answer.

209
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,320
Because you know the answer!

210
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,920
Because you know why!

211
00:13:08,920 --> 00:13:10,373
Because of you!

212
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:19,939
I'm sorry.

213
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,171
You know you're sly, right?

214
00:13:25,840 --> 00:13:28,440
You apologize as if you're inferior.

215
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:31,637
But I'm always the inferior.

216
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,797
Why did you come back?

217
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,240
Why did you meet me again?

218
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,559
Why did I come like a puppy

219
00:13:39,559 --> 00:13:41,795
when you beckoned me?

220
00:13:42,759 --> 00:13:44,854
I won't like you anymore.

221
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:47,082
I don't want to.

222
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:50,899
I don't want to be so cheap.

223
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:02,371
I'm the cheap one.

224
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:05,217
I'm the one who likes you.

225
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:14,190
Do you remember what you said there?

226
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:20,800
<i>It's like someone holding a kettle</i>

227
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:22,676
<i>and shouting "Boiling water" in a crowd.</i>

228
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:26,182
<i>If you don't want to move aside,</i>

229
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,840
<i>you need to prove</i>

230
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,563
<i>there's no boiling water in it.</i>

231
00:14:35,776 --> 00:14:39,440
<i>However, dwelling on trivialities‌</i>

232
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:41,175
<i>makes one unreasonable.</i>

233
00:14:41,759 --> 00:14:43,366
Let's just stop here.

234
00:14:45,399 --> 00:14:47,120
But I haven't replied yet.

235
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,840
You asked me so many questions.

236
00:14:48,840 --> 00:14:50,039
Don't you want my answer?

237
00:14:50,039 --> 00:14:51,202
No point.

238
00:14:52,781 --> 00:14:54,040
It's sly to ask "May I get by?"

239
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:56,080
when one is close to others.

240
00:14:56,080 --> 00:14:57,600
It sounds like an inquiry,

241
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:59,399
but has a preset answer.

242
00:14:59,399 --> 00:15:01,880
He just wants to look considerate.

243
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:03,880
We discussed this.

244
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:05,560
You don't want to know the answer.

245
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:07,780
You just want to condemn me, right?

246
00:15:08,840 --> 00:15:10,361
Then we're equally bad.

247
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,200
I'm not like you.

248
00:15:12,200 --> 00:15:14,113
Then let me finish.

249
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:20,120
A black-crowned night heron

250
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:24,201
would raise its crest in danger to bluff.

251
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,754
My least favorite bird.

252
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,477
Lies are my crest.
